{"tid":497688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海洋公園公佈16-17年度業績","createTime":"2017-12-13T04:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T10:14:29.000Z","uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf18fca7092614576cb4eeb80293ec5c3dd9acc","tid":497688,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"海洋公園公佈2016-2017財政年度業績<br />\n<br />\n- 入場人次為580萬，較去年度600萬稍微下跌<br />\n- 收入為港幣16億1980萬元，較去年度上升500萬元<br />\n- 全年度虧損為港幣2億3440萬元，較去年度下降670萬元<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園同時宣佈於2018年元旦起調整票價，平均加幅為9%<br />\n調整價格後成人門票為<span style=\"color: red;\">港幣480元</span>、小童則為<span style=\"color: red;\">港幣240元</span>，香港居民<span style=\"color: red;\">可享原價優惠至2018年2月底</span><br />\n香港居民另可享生日月份折扣優惠，於2018年間持香港身份證除可在生日當日免費入場外亦<span style=\"color: red;\">可於生日月份以85折購買最多4張正價入場門票</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/25358323_2056573397952619_2998835181756283715_o.jpg?oh=4f71d6147c2eec31060eff13a058ca54&amp;oe=5AD62618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F25358323_2056573397952619_2998835181756283715_o.jpg%3Foh%3D4f71d6147c2eec31060eff13a058ca54%26oe%3D5AD62618&h=ab161776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n關注我們的社交媒體，一起論盡香港旅遊事！<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TourisMan.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTourisMan.hk%2F&d=FDiDiXQ8KXKV%2BZxCjsWpTGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=eab2ed22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TourisMan.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n新設網站更方便、更集中！<br />\n<a href=\"https://johnlam1023.wixsite.com/tourismanhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjohnlam1023.wixsite.com%2Ftourismanhk&d=FDiDiXQ8KXKV%2BZxCjsWpTGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ecb03d42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://johnlam1023.wixsite.com/tourismanhk</a>"},{"pid":"0e6aaf0d4c5abd06